		{
			"id": "https://css-tip.com/color-wheel-gradient/",
			"url": "https://css-tip.com/color-wheel-gradient/",
			"title": "A color wheel with gradient",
			"content_html": "<p>Use <code>conic-gradient()</code> and the new color interpolation to create a nice color wheel ü§©</p>\n<pre class=\"language-css\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><br>  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">conic-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>in hsl longer hue<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>red 0 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><br><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<p>‚úÖ Tell the browser to take the longer route between red and red</p>\n<p>‚ùå No complex color combination</p>\n<p><picture><source type=\"image/avif\" srcset=\"https://css-tip.com/img/58NlxWHnqQ-593.avif 593w\"><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://css-tip.com/img/58NlxWHnqQ-593.webp 593w\"><img alt=\"A color wheel made conic-gradient\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://css-tip.com/img/58NlxWHnqQ-593.png\" width=\"593\" height=\"385\"></picture></p>\n<p class=\"codepen\" data-height=\"400\" data-default-tab=\"result\" data-slug-hash=\"XWPvgZo\" data-preview=\"true\" data-user=\"t_afif\" style=\"height: 400px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 2px solid; margin: 1em 0; padding: 1em;\">\n  <span>See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/t_afif/pen/XWPvgZo\">\n  Color wheel</a> by Temani Afif (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/t_afif\">@t_afif</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.</span>\n</p>\n<script async=\"\" src=\"https://cpwebassets.codepen.io/assets/embed/ei.js\"></script>\n<h2 id=\"related-links\" tabindex=\"-1\">Related Links <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"https://css-tip.com/color-wheel-gradient/\">#</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/articles/high-definition-css-color-guide/\">https://developer.chrome.com/articles/high-definition-css-color-guide/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-color-4/#hue-interpolation\">https://www.w3.org/TR/css-color-4/#hue-interpolation</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
			"date_published": "2023-04-03T00:00:00Z"
		}
