		{
			"id": "https://css-tip.com/hue-manipulation-color-mix/",
			"url": "https://css-tip.com/hue-manipulation-color-mix/",
			"title": "Hue manipulation using color-mix()",
			"content_html": "<p>Use the new <code>color-mix()</code> to manipulate the Hue of a color in the HSL color space</p>\n<pre class=\"language-css\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><br>  <span class=\"token property\">--color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <br>  <span class=\"token property\">--h</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* angle (from 0 to 360 without unit) */</span><br>  <br>  <span class=\"token property\">--new-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <br>    <span class=\"token function\">color-mix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>in hsl longer hue<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <br>      <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token function\">calc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--h<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>*1%/3.6<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><br>    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><br><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<p>The same can be done using relative colors but the support is still low:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-css\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.box</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><br>  <span class=\"token property\">--color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <br>  <span class=\"token property\">--h</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* angle (from 0 to 360 without unit) */</span><br>  <br>  <span class=\"token property\">--new-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">hsl</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>from <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token function\">calc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>h + <span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--h<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>*1deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> s l<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><br><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<p class=\"codepen\" data-height=\"300\" data-default-tab=\"result\" data-slug-hash=\"VwGNQEv\" data-preview=\"true\" data-user=\"t_afif\" style=\"height: 300px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 2px solid; margin: 1em 0; padding: 1em;\">\n  <span>See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/t_afif/pen/VwGNQEv\">\n  hue manipulation using color-mix()</a> by Temani Afif (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/t_afif\">@t_afif</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.</span>\n</p>\n<script async=\"\" src=\"https://cpwebassets.codepen.io/assets/embed/ei.js\"></script>\n<h2 id=\"related-links\" tabindex=\"-1\">Related Links <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"https://css-tip.com/hue-manipulation-color-mix/\">#</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/articles/high-definition-css-color-guide/\">https://developer.chrome.com/articles/high-definition-css-color-guide/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-color-5/#color-mix\">https://www.w3.org/TR/css-color-5/#color-mix</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
			"date_published": "2023-03-29T00:00:00Z"
		}
		,
		{
			"id": "https://css-tip.com/color-shades-color-mix/",
			"url": "https://css-tip.com/color-shades-color-mix/",
			"title": "Color shades using color-mix()",
			"content_html": "<p>Use the new <code>color-mix()</code> to create different shades from one color.</p>\n<p>Mix with ‚ö´Ô∏è black for a darker color and ‚ö™Ô∏è white for a lighter color</p>\n<pre class=\"language-css\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">html</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><br>  <span class=\"token property\">--color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8A9B0F<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* the main color */</span><br>  <span class=\"token property\">--color-light</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">color-mix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>in srgb<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>#fff 25%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><br>  <span class=\"token property\">--color-dark</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>  <span class=\"token function\">color-mix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>in srgb<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token function\">var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>--color<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>#000 25%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><br><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<p><picture><source type=\"image/avif\" srcset=\"https://css-tip.com/img/bQn4Q-ryeF-715.avif 715w\"><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://css-tip.com/img/bQn4Q-ryeF-715.webp 715w\"><img alt=\"3 color shades from one color\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://css-tip.com/img/bQn4Q-ryeF-715.png\" width=\"715\" height=\"371\"></picture></p>\n<p class=\"codepen\" data-height=\"300\" data-default-tab=\"result\" data-slug-hash=\"ExeMOPV\" data-preview=\"true\" data-user=\"t_afif\" style=\"height: 300px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 2px solid; margin: 1em 0; padding: 1em;\">\n  <span>See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/t_afif/pen/ExeMOPV\">\n  Color shades using  color-mix()</a> by Temani Afif (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/t_afif\">@t_afif</a>)\n  on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.</span>\n</p>\n<script async=\"\" src=\"https://cpwebassets.codepen.io/assets/embed/ei.js\"></script>\n<h2 id=\"related-links\" tabindex=\"-1\">Related Links <a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"https://css-tip.com/color-shades-color-mix/\">#</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/articles/high-definition-css-color-guide/\">https://developer.chrome.com/articles/high-definition-css-color-guide/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css-color-5/#color-mix\">https://www.w3.org/TR/css-color-5/#color-mix</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
			"date_published": "2023-03-28T00:00:00Z"
		}
